text: Stéphane Gomes Gonçalves (born 2 May 1996) is a Portuguese footballer who plays for Echallens, as a Left winger. ==Football career== On 22 May 2015, Gonçalves made his professional debut with Lausanne-Sport in a 2014–15 Swiss Challenge League match against Le Mont. He left Lausanne-Sport in 2015, going on to play for Stade Lausanne Ouchy, Vevey Sports, Azzurri 90 LS and FC Echallens ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Association football wingers Category:Swiss Challenge League players Category:FC Lausanne- Sport players
